---
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <div class="text-3xl">Mission</div>
      <div class="font-medium italic">Who are we and what are we about?</div>
    </div>
    <div class="h-0.5 bg-gray-800 rounded-full"></div>
    <ul class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
      <Section title="What are we trying to do?">
        <div class="text-lg font-medium">
          We want to build tools to provide structure, community and the purpose
          that is found in opportunities like College and Church. Not everyone
          has access to those resources, so we want to provide the opportunities
          for those local communities to thrive.
        </div>
      </Section>
      <Section title="Why are we doing this?">
        <div class="text-lg font-medium">
          We believe that everyone deserves to feel like they belong. Belonging
          comes from community. Intentional, lasting community is becoming
          harder and harder to find. Our goal is to make that process easier for
          everyone. If we can help even two people connect who wouldn't have
          connected without us, we acomplished our mission.
        </div>
      </Section>
      <Section title="How Do We Make Money">
        <div class="text-lg font-medium">
          Currently? We don't. We have plans to release some software products
          that we will offer a fremium service for, but until then we are funded
          through donations.
        </div>
      </Section>
      <Section title="Core Values">
        <div>
          <ul>
            <li class="text-lg font-medium">- People Over Profit</li>
            <li class="text-lg font-medium">- Lifelong Learning</li>
            <li class="text-lg font-medium">- Empowering Individuals</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </Section>
      <Section title="The Team">
        <div></div>
      </Section>
    </ul>

    <style>
      * {
        @apply text-xl;
      }
    </style>
  </div>
</Layout>
